data.description: BRAND NEW FLOORING THROUGH OUT ENTIRE HOME! This exceptional property boasts 4 bedrooms, 2 bathrooms. Upon entering, you'll immediately appreciate the open floor plan and the combination of stained concrete and tile flooring adds a touch of modern elegance while ensuring low maintenance and durability. The abundant natural light streaming through the new windows creates a warm and inviting atmosphere throughout the home. Kitchen is a true chef's delight, featuring ample counter space and modern appliances. The home's spacious bedrooms offer comfortable retreats for rest and relaxation. One of the standout features of this property is its large lot, offering plenty of outdoor space for recreation and entertainment. Whether you envision hosting lively gatherings or simply enjoying quiet moments in the fresh air, this backyard provides the perfect backdrop.
